@rabbah I think I understand now better. I agree from the invoker there is no need to do port mapping.

We already have a case where we detect Mac but only from test system
https://github.com/openwhisk/openwhisk/blob/master/tests/src/actionContainers/ActionContainer.scala#L85

```
    private lazy val dockerCmd: String = {
        val hostStr = if (WhiskProperties.onMacOSX()) {
            s" --host tcp://${WhiskProperties.getMainDockerEndpoint()} "
        } else {
            " "
        }
        s"$dockerBin $hostStr"
    }
```

